Package: readihme
Title: Access IHME SDG Data Through R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Beth", "Firipis", , "bfiripis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-3477-5003"))
Description: Provides easy access to the Institute for Health Metrics and 
    Evaluation (IHME) Sustainable Development Goals (SDG) API. Functions allow 
    users to retrieve SDG indicator data, metadata, and perform common data 
    analysis tasks with IHME data.
